<body lang=EN-IN style='tab-interval:36.0pt;word-wrap:break-word'>

<div class=WordSection1>

<h1><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Project
Documentation<o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Technologies Used,
Framework<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Backend Framework:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Spring Boot 3.2.5<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Programming Language:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Java 17<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Frontend Framework:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Thymeleaf (Template Engine), HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Security:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Spring Security<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Database Architecture:</span></b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Spring Data JPA
     (Hibernate)<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Database Server:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Microsoft SQL Server (MSSQL)<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l13 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>AI Integration:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Google Gemini AI API<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.1 Frontend
Implementation<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.1.1 Environment
Setup<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l9 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Web Browser:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, or Microsoft Edge.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l9 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Development Tool:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> IDE like IntelliJ IDEA or VS Code.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l9 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Dependencies:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Webjars, Custom CSS/JS frameworks.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.1.2 Structure of
the Project<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>The frontend is structured using the MVC architecture.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Templates Directory:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Located in </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>src/main/resources/templates</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>, containing Thymeleaf
     HTML pages.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Static Resources:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Located in </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>src/main/resources/static</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>, containing CSS
     stylesheets, JavaScript files, and images.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Dynamic Content:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Pages dynamically render data passed from backend
     controllers using Thymeleaf syntax.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.1.3 Execution
Procedure<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>The frontend runs embedded within the Spring Boot
     application server (Apache Tomcat).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Once the backend server starts, the application UI is
     accessible via </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>http://localhost:8080/</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Users navigate through hyperlinked menus triggering
     HTTP requests to the controller.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.2 Backend
Implementation<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.2.1 Environment
Setup<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Java Development Kit (JDK):</span></b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Version 17 installed
     and configured.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Build Tool:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Apache Maven for dependency management.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>IDE:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> IntelliJ IDEA, Eclipse, or VS Code configured with
     Spring Boot extensions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.2.2 Structure of
the Project<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>config</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Configuration classes (e.g., Security, AI
     configurations).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>controller</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: REST APIs and view controllers mapping web endpoints.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>model</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: JPA entity classes representing database tables.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>repository</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Data Access Layer interfaces extending </span><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>JpaRepository</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>service</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Business logic handling user operations and API
     integrations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l8 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>security</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Authentication providers, session handling, password
     encoding.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.2.3 Execution
Procedure<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Execute </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>mvn
     clean install</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     to build the application and download dependencies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Run the main class </span><code><span style='font-size:
     10.0pt'>PortalApplication.java</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> via IDE.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Alternatively, run </span><code><span style='font-size:
     10.0pt'>mvn spring-boot:run</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> from the command line.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Check console logs to ensure Tomcat started on port
     8080 without errors.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.3 Database
Implementation<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.3.1 Database
Configuration<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>The system connects to MS SQL Server using the </span><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>mssql-jdbc</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> driver.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Configured in </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>application.properties</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: </span><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>spring.datasource.url=jdbc:sqlserver://localhost;instanceName=SQLEXPRESS;databaseName=CampusRecruitment</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Integrated Security (Windows Authentication) is
     enabled.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Hibernate is configured to automatically update the DDL
     schemas.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.3.2 Schema
Structure<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l14 level1 lfo9;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>The relational database schema enforces referential
     integrity using primary and foreign keys.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l14 level1 lfo9;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Relationships:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> One-to-One (Users to Profiles), One-to-Many (Employers
     to Jobs, Jobs to Applications).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3.3.3 Tables
Created<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>users</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Core table for Authentication and Roles.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>login_audit_log</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Tracks user login
     sessions, timestamps, and IP addresses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>otp_verification_log</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Logs OTP emails,
     purposes, and expiry times.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>student_profiles</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Stores detailed
     student metrics, skills, and resumes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>employer_profiles</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Contains company
     details and admin approval state.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>jobs</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Postings containing requirements, descriptions, and
     salary details.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>applications</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Tracks student applications and AI match scores.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>interviews</span></code><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>: Interview scheduling, times, and meeting links.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>assessment_questions</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Multiple choice
     questions attached to specific job postings.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo10;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>notifications</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: System alerts and
     in-app messages.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4. Project
Architecture<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.2 DataFlow
Diagram<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo11;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Client Tier:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Web Browser or Mobile App interacts with the UI.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo11;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Presentation Tier:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Spring Controllers handle HTTP requests and return
     Thymeleaf views or JSON responses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo11;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Business Tier:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Services execute core logic, communicate with Gemini
     AI, and dispatch Emails.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo11;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Data Access Tier:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> Repositories interact with the database using
     Hibernate/JPA.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo11;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Database Tier:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'> MS SQL Server stores and retrieves persistent records.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.3 Module 1: User
&amp; Authentication Management<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo12;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Manages registration, secure login, and access control.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo12;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Enforces role-based access control (Admin, Employer,
     Student).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo12;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Features email-based OTP verification for enhanced
     security.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo12;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Comprehensive user profile management for both students
     and employers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.4 Module 2: Job
Management &amp; Application Tracking<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l10 level1 lfo13;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Employers can create, update, and manage job postings.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l10 level1 lfo13;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Students can browse, filter, and apply for active jobs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l10 level1 lfo13;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Automated tracking of application statuses (Pending,
     Shortlisted, Interview Scheduled, Selected).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l10 level1 lfo13;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>AI integration to generate match scores between
     candidate resumes and job requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.5 Module 3:
Assessment &amp; Interview System<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l11 level1 lfo14;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Built-in assessment modules mapping technical MCQs to
     specific job roles.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l11 level1 lfo14;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Scheduling system for interviews assigning dates,
     times, and video meeting links.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l11 level1 lfo14;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Automated email and in-app notifications to update
     students regarding their progress and upcoming reminders.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5. Advantages of
this Project<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>a) Streamlined
Recruitment Workflow<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p>Provides a centralized digital platform that reduces manual intervention,
seamlessly bridging the gap between educational institutions and corporate
hiring teams.</p>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>b) Enhanced
Security &amp; Tracking<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p>Features robust security mechanisms including OTP verification, strict
role-based access restrictions, and detailed audit logs for tracking user
logins and critical application updates.</p>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>6. Disadvantages<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l12 level1 lfo15;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Dependency on
     Third-Party APIs:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     Core functionalities like AI resume matching and automated email
     notifications rely completely on Google Gemini and Gmail SMTP servers.
     Outages in these services affect application functionality.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l12 level1 lfo15;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Internet Requirement:</span></b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Being a
     cloud-integrated web application, it cannot operate without a stable and
     continuous internet connection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l12 level1 lfo15;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Database Load &amp;
     Scalability:</span></b><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     Storing complex data like resumes, extensive assessments, and continuous
     audit logs in a single relational database may require active maintenance,
     archiving, and scaling optimizations as the user base expands.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

</div>

</body>

</html>
